RISK 2: ATTRACTION OF HOSTILE ATTENTION
  Probability: Very Low (<0.01%)
  Impact: Catastrophic (planetary security)
  Mitigation: No Earth location data in message
  Justification: Energy cost for aggression prohibitive

RISK 3: THEOLOGICAL CONTROVERSY
  Probability: High (60%)
  Impact: Medium (social division)
  Mitigation: Interfaith advisory board, inclusive framing
  Outreach: Public education on scientific spirituality

RISK 4: RESOURCE ALLOCATION CRITICISM
  Probability: Medium (30%)
  Impact: Low (voluntary funding)
  Mitigation: Crowdfunding model, educational benefits
  Transparency: Complete public accounting

RISK 5: SIGNAL CONTAMINATION
  Probability: Low (5%)
  Impact: Low (message integrity)
  Mitigation: Triple transmission, error correction
  Verification: Pre-transmission simulation
```

